/* Created by Captain Kniples the Fourth */
/* For funsies */
/* Created 2024 05 05 */
/* This is a 4v4 map only */

/* This map is designed around the idea of teams trading resources with each other (called slinging in extreme cases). 
   Teams have one player who has access to lots of gold and wood, but limited food. The other three players have access
   to lots of food and wood, but very limited gold. As such, they need to send each other resources to balance their economies.
   As such, "slinging" (which is an extreme case of team resource trading) should be allowed from dark age. */


/* Add extra elevation to the inner ring - shouldnt be hard, just make it so the fill land is higher but has zone avoidance */

/* ***********************************************************************************************
 *  A possible future edition of this map could be making it so that the "gold player"           *
 *  (i.e. the player with access to excessive amounts of gold) starts with more villagers than   *
 *  the others. This would be easy to implement and create a different dynamic to any other map  *
 *  as one player on each team would be given a head start on all the other players              *
 *********************************************************************************************** */



#const ONGRID_PLACEHOLDER 1613
#const TREE_50_WOOD       1350


<PLAYER_SETUP>
direct_placement
behavior_version 1






<LAND_GENERATION>

base_terrain DIRT


/* Base Terrain */
create_land
{
  terrain_type          DIRT 
  base_size             2
  land_position         30 50 
  land_percent          100 
  base_elevation        1
  zone                  1
}
